## 7. API Endpoints Summary

-   **POST /api/client/join**: Join a group with a code.
-   **POST /api/client/:groupCode/upload-selfie**: Upload selfie for matching.
-   **POST /api/groups**: Create a new group (Photographer).
-   **POST /api/groups/:id/upload**: Upload photos to group (Photographer).
-   **GET /api/photo/:photoId/download**: Secure download link for a photo.
-   **POST /api/signup / /api/login**: User/Photographer authentication.

